2. the pilot is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the fan of country is between the dressmaker and the owner of the horse##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Job          | dressmaker | entrepreneur | pilot    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
