There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in june##2
5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| Birthday         | february  | september       | june |
| Music-Genre   | reggae   | blues         | ambient     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

