4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the security-guard and the person who growsbegonia##2
6. the person who growslily is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
