2. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person eating garlic is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
